OL,3,CMan jailed for killing vulnerable
OL,4,Cuncle in drunken rage
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after dragging
OL,7,Fhis vulnerable uncle down two flights
OL,8,Fof stairs, leaving him with fatal head
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,FLiam Elms, 41, from Liverpool, had
OL,12,Fbeen caring for Paul Lavery, 58, who
OL,13,Fhad only recently been discharged from
OL,14,Fhospital after having brain surgery.
OL,16,FBut despite knowing his condition,
OL,17,FElms attacked Mr Lavery in a drunken
OL,18,Frage, repeatedly hit him in the face,
OL,19,Fand then dragged him down two flights
OL,20,Fof stairs by his legs.
