OL,3,CMan jailed for killing vulnerable
OL,4,Cuncle in drunken rage
OL,6,FThe victim was found with serious
OL,7,Finjuries outside a property on Eaton
OL,8,FRoad, West Derby, at 1am on 24 January
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FMr Lavery was rushed to the Royal
OL,12,FLiverpool Hospital before being
OL,13,Ftransferred to the Walton Centre,
OL,14,Fhaving suffered a "serious head
OL,15,Finjury". He died days later.
OL,17,FMerseyside Police said Elms was
OL,18,F"highly aggressive" and in a
OL,19,F"threatening state" when they arrested
OL,20,Fhim shortly after.
