OL,3,CMan jailed for killing vulnerable
OL,4,Cuncle in drunken rage
OL,6,FHaving returned to his uncle's home at
OL,7,Faround 11:30pm on 23 January 23 after
OL,8,Fa night out drinking with his
OL,9,Fgirlfriend, he stated that he noticed
OL,10,Faround #80 in cash was missing from a
OL,11,Fpaper bag and that fresh bottles of
OL,12,Fvodka had appeared in the flat.
OL,14,FUnder questioning from his counsel
OL,15,FMichael Brady KC during the trial,
OL,16,FElms alleged that Mr Lavery got up to
OL,17,Fuse the bathroom at one stage and
OL,18,Faccidentally banged his head on the
OL,19,Fliving room radiator.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
