OL,3,CMan jailed for killing vulnerable
OL,4,Cuncle in drunken rage
OL,6,FHe said he attempted to convince his
OL,7,Funcle - who had undergone a brain
OL,8,Foperation in December 2023 - to go to
OL,9,Fthe hospital.
OL,11,FBut when his uncle refused, Elms
OL,12,Freported that Lavey lashed out and
OL,13,F"back handed" him across the face.
OL,15,FHe added: "He wanted to keep carrying
OL,16,Fon drinking. We argued over it. I
OL,17,Fslapped him in the face. (His nose)
OL,18,Fwas bleeding." Elms added: "I can't
OL,19,Fjustify it, what I done. I loved him."
