OL,3,CMan jailed for killing vulnerable
OL,4,Cuncle in drunken rage
OL,6,FJudge Cummings told Elms: "I am sure
OL,7,Fanyone who knows your uncle's medical
OL,8,Fhistory will have recognised there was
OL,9,Fa high risk of serious injury and
OL,10,Fdeath."
OL,12,FMerseyside Police, Detective Inspector
OL,13,FDaniel McWhinnie said: "I'd like to
OL,14,Fthank Paul's family for their patience
OL,15,Fand bravery during this heart-breaking
OL,16,Fprocess, one made all the harder to
OL,17,Fbear by the refusal of Elms to admit
OL,18,Fwhat he had done.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
